{"id":240714,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-长沙拆迁受害人谢燕被刑事拘留，周三桂/","date":"2012-07-18T08:01:45Z","modified":"2012-07-18T08:01:45Z","title":"维权网 | 长沙拆迁受害人谢燕被刑事拘留，周三桂遭扣押殴打（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span> </span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><br /><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张成报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>，因为拆迁矛盾，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span>长沙市公安局岳麓区分局岳麓派出所所长谢良安带领十几人到岳麓街道靳江村的拆迁户谢燕家把她强行带走，后来谢燕给表妹周佳打电话说她被打了，受不了了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>岳麓派出所所长谢良安又打电话找周三桂，即周佳的父亲，谢燕的舅舅。周佳接到电话，所长谢良安说：“周三桂去哪了，他来我派出所不？”周佳说：“他又没犯什么法，为什么要去你那</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span><span>”</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日</span><span>上午，派出所向周三桂下达了传唤通知书，周三桂</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>点左右到达岳麓派出所，晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>点才到家。谢所所威胁说，时间很急，要周三桂和拆迁指挥部协商，协商成了就算了，在晚上两点之前没搞好，就把谢燕送进监狱。下一个就是你周三桂，按“伪造公文罪”处罚。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>当晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>点，岳麓派出所所长谢良安打电话问周三桂怎么样了，同意不？周三桂说不同意。很快谢良安带领二十几名没有制服编号的人把周三桂从自己家中抓走，并带上了手铐。未出示任何证件手续。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日</span><span>下午，周三桂回到家中，表示被警方成“大”字状戴手铐脚镣，并且遭遇殴打。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>期间，谢燕一直在没有任何手续的情况下遭到关押。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日</span><span>，谢燕的丈夫李正武第三次到岳麓派出所要求放人，周警官给了一份谢燕的《刑事拘留通知书》。拘留书中称，谢燕“因为涉嫌伪造证件、印章罪”被刑事拘留，羁押于长沙市公安局监所管理支队第一看守所。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>周佳电话</span><span> <span lang=\"EN-US\">15116407402</span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-EfzsoW7v29k/UAZoI6WaUjI/AAAAAAAAJZA/sU5d-d0dvqU/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"216\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-EfzsoW7v29k/UAZoI6WaUjI/AAAAAAAAJZA/sU5d-d0dvqU/s320/3.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/--giZ_hOBr5g/UAZoL3ueSbI/AAAAAAAAJZI/Sd_QB1MQ_mo/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/--giZ_hOBr5g/UAZoL3ueSbI/AAAAAAAAJZI/Sd_QB1MQ_mo/s320/1.jpg\" width=\"224\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-DugI1yEpGIA/UAZoObXFOdI/AAAAAAAAJZQ/FiU7Jh4Oock/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-DugI1yEpGIA/UAZoObXFOdI/AAAAAAAAJZQ/FiU7Jh4Oock/s320/2.jpg\" width=\"251\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-4064756401983793483?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/92297adb3.jpg-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}